[normal]1.
[normal]5
[normal] 
[normal]Our
[normal] joint response concentrate
[normal]s
[normal] upon implications of
[normal] changes
[normal] in respect of Registered 
[normal]Providers
[normal],
[normal] and 
[normal]vulnerable claimants – particularly those with disabilities and within supported accommodation
[normal], not all of which will come within the current definition of exempt accommodation
[normal]. 
[normal]We have also responded on the treatme
[normal]nt of housing costs within Universal Credit
[normal]; and made additional observations on future implications for older people.
